{"tid":1839404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係嚟自一個月後嘅香港人","createTime":"2020-01-24T11:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T12:06:35.000Z","uid":330057,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c9dd28e94a94dc45c2e489bac8993876cb99ff","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"呢個月發生咗好多嘢，而家已經係三月<br />\n從一開始<br />\n嚟自武漢嘅中國人坐高鐵之後入住太子嗰啲賓館<br />\n佢哋都係潛伏期嘅患者冇發燒，所以成功過境<br />\n所以好快太子開始咗第一宗社區爆發。<br />\n唔使一個星期<br />\n聯合同瑪麗醫院已經爆滿懷疑感染個案<br />\n北潭涌隔離營亦都開始運作<br />\n<br />\n咁我講緊係條街係咩環境<br />\n當初有商家話封港嘅話會造成嚴重嘅經濟損失<br />\n但係香港爆發咗之後，我行落條街度10間鋪7間冇開，原來香港一旦社區爆發，其實係冇分別。喺尖沙咀行到去旺角連一個遊客都見唔到.....啲鋪頭都係冇開門。條街顯得好冷清。<br />\n<br />\n同時學校亦都出現學生同老師交叉感染個案....<br />\n好似有好多學生嘅家長因為返咗大陸探親，直接感染到佢哋嘅細路仔，然後細路仔又將啲病毒帶返學校。<br />\n最後去到咁嘅地步政府先宣佈停課.....一個月<br />\n<br />\n唉，前兩日睇到一個新聞先誇張，其中一名住院中國患者竟然扯開香港醫生同護士嘅口罩再噴口水，話佢哋冇心醫好佢.....<br />\n跟住今日仲睇到條片，又或者係咁噴口水落電梯啲掣到.....<br />\n唔知係冰山一角定係點啦<br />\n<br />\n跟住呢個月仲發生咗好多好多嘢<br />\n我只係太心痛，先至忍唔住過嚟同你地講"},{"pid":"2c776c37bfe780c492054e8b39f24fca7ad7853a","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"以上故事純屬虛構<br />\n但係點到即止啦<br />\n我都唔想再寫埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80162df50f10b01862a4b7fd9390778c47c4cd83","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"上面已經封咗五座城<br />\n面對呢個無能嘅政府，我哋只可以自救<br />\n呢一刻各界互相團結有冇可能？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GZxxrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GZxxrf.jpg&h=98d86e5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef715b7e4305f931b88bee23040a6ce419dbcb3f","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f4d07b1a0c0776cdfd5ae1cdd11db5d3024c98","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:53:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">來了，他們來了</span></span>"},{"pid":"229a432ff3cab3c3619dfccf18bc39973d3af60f","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:54:40.000Z","msg":"Push pls"},{"pid":"81d126e83a31ec7c1cecde1c735eb40cd6ec1858","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66ac7155944aafe3e61e05bf9d22d766caab7ad2","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"85019122848079d9f301b4d9889a4477b2c63660","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"006270e1f3fd0cec8fa0bec16aee794e4c9b9c97","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔通真係冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c99ff6f6c2ff28ed11ed501c328ab15a3bf560","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06276e81d12e75b9622be3a626d89cdfd438092e","tid":1839404,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"244f7430325951b15d3874d6ff1a05e95a7aa04d","tid":1839404,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=